## **“Time Travelling Soul Wizard”**

דער איז    א    тайм    травелін    솔    wys-ard  
In א    dood    trí    in    買    ярд  
Hē's    sitten    דער    mit    hīs    legs    krost  
Hīs    hūd    iz    blå    līk    ðe    sí  
Hīs    robe    iz    flói-ing    līk    א    strøm  
Hīs    baard    iz    sō    lang    it    rīċ-es    hīs    knē-s  
And    hē's    sō    ould    hē    dūs-n't    ēven  
    knāw    wat    Jahr    it    iz  
But    hē's    réal  
愛'm    tellin'    有    hē's    réal  
Hē    said    if    有    want    to    escāp    ðe    māter Ix  
有've    gotta    bikam    א    тайм-травелін    솔    wys-ard  
有've    gotta  
Bikam    א    тайм-травелін    솔    wys-ard  
有've    gotta    bikam    א    тайм-травелін    솔    wys-ard  
有've    gotta    bikam    א    тайм-травелін    솔    wys-ard  
有've...    }有've...}    (有've....) Got tu...

**STEP 1: GHOST-ENGLISH (Original)**

There is a time traveling soul wizard  
In a dead tree in my yard  
He's sitting there with his legs crossed  
His hood is blue like the sea  
His robe is flowing like a stream  
His beard is so long it reaches his knees  
And he's so old he doesn't even know what year it is  
But he's real  
I'm telling you he's real  
He said if you want to escape the matrix  
You've got to become a time-traveling soul wizard  
You’ve got to  
Become a time-traveling soul wizard  
You’ve got to become a time-traveling soul wizard  
You’ve got to become a time-traveling soul wizard  
You’ve… You’ve… You’ve… Got to

